imdb.plot outline: Leah Monti's GET DOWN is a one-hour Futuristic reality based show that is a Youth-Reality Talk, Fashion and Dance Show with Celebrity Musical Guests performances, along with mini interviews and presentations of Fashion and Art from all over the World. Also Highlighting Leah Monti's seven attractive and inspirational Dance/Interns who are hungry for fame, while enduring all the trials and tribulations that come with being in front of the camera. With the high drama of the cast voting each week for the upcoming episode's to be Head Choreographer , the action is intense as we see what each of these interns will do to succeed.
imdb.title: Leah Monti's GET DOWN
plot: FEATURING. Hip Hop and Rap.House meets Fashion. Celebrity Talk and Special Guests...XO.::Leah Monti Litzner
